    "title": "Ser, Estar, and Other Equivalents of To Be",
    "html": "<h1>The basics of <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">SER</span> and <span style=\"color: rgb(196, 99, 116);\">ESTAR</span></h1>\r\n<h2 jscontroller=\"Ae65rd\" jsaction=\"touchstart:UrsOsc; click:KjsqPd; focusout:QZoaZ; mouseover:y0pDld; mouseout:dq0hvd;fv1Rjc:jbFSOd;CrfLRd:SzACGe;\" class=\"CjVfdc\"><span class=\"C9DxTc \">What is the basic meaning of<span>&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"C9DxTc \" style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">SER</span><span class=\"C9DxTc \"><span>&nbsp;</span>&amp;<span>&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"C9DxTc \" style=\"color: rgb(196, 99, 116);\">ESTAR</span><span class=\"C9DxTc \">?</span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\"><strong><span class=\"C9DxTc \">SER</span></strong></span><span class=\"C9DxTc \"> expresses&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">the essence</span>&nbsp;</strong>of someone or something. Think of&nbsp;<strong>e</strong><strong>ssence</strong> as any quality or attribute that <strong>defines</strong>&nbsp;<em>how&nbsp;</em>someone or something is perceived. This is what&nbsp;<strong>SER</strong> is at its core.</span><span class=\"C9DxTc \"></span></p>\r\n<details class=\"pp-accordion\" open=\"\">\r\n<summary>💬Common examples that describe<em style=\"display: inline !important;\">essence</em>with <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">SER</span></summary>\r\n<div class=\"pp-accordion-body\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Identity</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Juan y Carla <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">son</span> mis mejores amigos.</strong><span><br></span><em>Juan and Carla are my best friends.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Esta pel&iacute;cula <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">es</span> mi favorita.</strong><span><br></span><em>This movie is my favorite.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Origen</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Mi abuela <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">es</span>&nbsp;de M&eacute;xico.</strong><span><br></span><span> </span><em>My grandmother is from Mexico.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Estos vinos <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">son</span>&nbsp;de Argentina.</strong><span><br></span><span> </span><em>These wines are from Argentina.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Brand</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Mi celular <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">es</span>&nbsp;un iPhone.</strong><span><br></span><em>My cell is an iPhone.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Esos zapatos <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">son</span>&nbsp;Nike.</strong><span><br></span><span> </span><em>Those shoes are Nike.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Personality</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Mi hermana <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">es </span>muy extrovertida.</strong><span><br></span><em>My sister is very outgoing.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Marcos <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">es </span>una persona muy paciente.</strong><span><br></span><em>Marcos is a very patient person.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Material</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Esta mesa <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">es </span>de madera.</strong><span><br></span><em>This table is made of wood.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Mis anillos <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">son</span> de plata.</strong><span><br></span><em>My rings are made of silver.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Color</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Mi coche <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">es </span>rojo.</strong><span><br></span><em>My car is red.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Estas paredes <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">son</span> blancas.</strong><span><br></span><em>These walls are white.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Qualities</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>El caf&eacute; <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">es </span>amargo sin az&uacute;car.</strong><span><br></span><em>Coffee is bitter without sugar.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Su voz <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">es </span>muy suave.</strong><span><br></span><em>Her/His voice is very soft.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Profession</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Mi pap&aacute; <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">es </span>m&eacute;dico.</strong><span><br></span><em>My dad is a doctor.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Ellos <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">son</span> profesores de historia.</strong><span><br></span><em>They are history teachers.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Personal Relationships</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Carolina <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">es </span>mi prima.</strong><span><br></span><em>Carolina is my cousin.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Nosotros&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">somos&nbsp;</span>novios.</strong><span><br></span><em>We're a couple (boyfriend &amp; girlfriend/boyfriends)</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Category</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Los gatos <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">son</span> mam&iacute;feros.</strong><span><br></span><em>Cats are mammals.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Este libro <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">es </span>una novela de ciencia ficci&oacute;n.</strong><span><br></span><em>This book is a science fiction novel.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Shape</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>La mesa <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">es </span>redonda.</strong><span><br></span><em>The table is round.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Mis gafas <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">son</span> rectangulares.</strong><span><br></span><em>My glasses are rectangular.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Dates</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Hoy <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">es </span>martes.</strong><span><br></span><em>Today is Tuesday.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Mi cumplea&ntilde;os <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">es </span>el 10 de abril.</strong><span><br></span><em>My birthday is on April 10th.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Times</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Ahora <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">es&nbsp;</span>la una y media de la tarde.</strong><span><br></span><em>Right now, it is 1:30 in the afternoon.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">Son</span> las 17 horas. / Son las cinco de la tarde.</strong><span><br></span><em>It's 5:00 pm.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><span></span><strong>La reuni&oacute;n <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">es&nbsp;</span>a las cinco.</strong><span><br></span><em>The meeting is at five.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</details>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(196, 99, 116);\"><strong><span class=\"C9DxTc \">ESTAR</span></strong></span><span class=\"C9DxTc \"> expresses&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(196, 99, 116);\">the situation</span>&nbsp;</strong>of someone or something. This is&nbsp;<strong>ESTAR&nbsp;</strong>at its core.</span><span class=\"C9DxTc \"></span></p>\r\n<details class=\"pp-accordion\" open=\"\">\r\n<summary><span class=\"C9DxTc \">⚠️Problems with traditional explanations</span></summary>\r\n<div class=\"pp-accordion-body\">\r\n<p><span class=\"C9DxTc \">You may have seen or heard explanations like \"<em>SER</em><em> is used with permanent characteristics and ESTAR with temporary ones.\"</em> This usually holds up, but also causes confusion when you run into examples like these:</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong><span class=\"C9DxTc \">El Everest <span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: rgb(196, 99, 116);\">est&aacute;</span> en el sur de Asia, cerca de</span></strong><span class=\"C9DxTc \"> <strong>Nepal.</strong><em><br></em><em>Mt. Everest is in Southern Asia, near Nepal.</em></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span class=\"C9DxTc \">The location of Mount Everest seems like a permanent feature &mdash; barring a devastating asteroid impact, war, or some other catastrophe &mdash; so why did we use&nbsp;ESTAR&nbsp;instead of&nbsp;SER? Further on in this guide, you'll see why we think of the location of places as&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(196, 99, 116);\"><strong>situational</strong></span> instead of as&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">essential</span></strong>.</span><span class=\"C9DxTc \"></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</details>\r\n<div style=\"position: relative; width: 100%; height: 0; padding-top: 56.2500%; padding-bottom: 0; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px 0 rgba(63,69,81,0.16); margin-top: 1.6em; margin-bottom: 0.9em; overflow: hidden; border-radius: 8px; will-change: transform;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.canva.com/design/DAGOfM70F9E/BQDirBfUXRbjR88Eh4Et3A/view?embed\" allow=\"fullscreen\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" width=\"\" height=\"\" style=\"position: absolute; width: 100%; height: 100%; top: 0; left: 0; border: none; padding: 0; margin: 0;\" loading=\"lazy\">  </iframe></div>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"C9DxTc \"></span></p>\r\n<h2 id=\"h.sm60g21c1cxj_l\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"zfr3Q JYVBee CDt4Ke \"></h2>",
